l"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="search-icon"><use xlink:href="#svg-search"></use></svg></label> </div> <div id="search-results" class="search-results"></div> </div> <nav aria-label="Auxiliary" class="aux-nav"> <ul class="aux-nav-list"> <li class="aux-nav-list-item"> <a href="//betaclub.org/" class="site-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" > National Beta Club </a> </li> <li class="aux-nav-list-item"> <a href="//sponsors.betaclub.org/" class="site-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" > Sponsors Site </a> </li> <li class="aux-nav-list-item"> <a href="//shop.betaclub.org/" class="site-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" > Beta Shop </a> </li> </ul> </nav> </div> <div id="main-content-wrap" class="main-content-wrap"> <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="breadcrumb-nav"> <ol class="breadcrumb-nav-list"> <li class="breadcrumb-nav-list-item"><a href="">Handbook</a></li> <li class="breadcrumb-nav-list-item"><a href="">National Exhibitions</a></li> <li class="breadcrumb-nav-list-item"><span>Create and Animate</span></li> </ol> </nav> <div id="main-content" class="main-content" role="main"> <h1 id="create-and-animate"> <a href="#create-and-animate" class="anchor-heading" aria-labelledby="create-and-animate"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#svg-link"></use></svg></a> Create and Animate </h1> <p>Teams of 2 to 4 students will create a high-quality, well-designed digital animation to be shared on a web-based platform. Electricity and internet will not be provided. **Entry must be completed prior to convention. **</p> <p>Each club may register one team for this exhibition. Exhibition is limited to the first 100 clubs that register for National Convention. Register early in order to ensure your club’s participation.</p> <h2 id="competition-guidelines"> <a href="#competition-guidelines" class="anchor-heading" aria-labelledby="competition-guidelines"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#svg-link"></use></svg></a> Competition Guidelines </h2> <ol> <li>A prompt and rules for the entry will be emailed to all registered clubs.</li> <li>Teams of 2 to 4 students will create a high-quality, welldesigned digital animation to be shared on a web based platform.</li> <li>Teams must provide their own computer or device.</li> <li>Teams will not be allowed to use the internet during the exhibition’s presentation. If an internet connection is needed, please bring a hotspot.</li> <li>Electricity will not be provided.</li> </ol> <h2 id="judging-criteria"> <a href="#judging-criteria" class="anchor-heading" aria-labelledby="judging-criteria"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#svg-link"></use></svg></a> Judging Criteria </h2> <ul> <li>Creativity &amp; Originality - 20 pts.</li> <li>Design - 20 pts.</li> <li>Technical Competency- 20 pts.</li> <li>Craftsmanship - 20 pts.</li> <li>Presentation Skills -20 pts.</li> </ul> <h2 id="education-connections"> <a href="#education-connections" class="anchor-heading" aria-labelledby="education-connections"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#svg-link"></use></svg></a> Education Connections </h2> <ul> <li>Knowledge of Web Design</li> <li>Creativity and Innovation</li> <li>Communication and Collaboration</li> <li>Real World Application</li> <li>Graphic Design and Marketing</li> <li>Computer Programming</li> </ul> <hr> <footer> <footer> <a href="#" class="back-to-top">Back to Top</a> Page last modified at: 03/19/2024 <br><br> Copyright &copy; 2022 National Beta Club. <!-- Distributed by an <a href=\"https://github.com/pmarsceill/just-the-docs/tree/master/LICENSE.txt\">MIT license.</a> --> </footer> <div class="d-flex mt-2"> </div> </footer> </div> </div> <a href="#" id="search-button" class="search-button"> <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon"><use xlink:href="#svg-search"></use></svg> </a> <div class="search-overlay"></div> </div> </body> </html>
